----------------------
FREE THE AMIGA PROJECT
----------------------

I want to start a project, that is called FREE THE AMIGA.
I believe, that one strength of the AMIGA is the huge
amount of freeware software. This makes the AMIGA
outstanding, since we are not in UNIX worlds here....

I just want to remember every coder, that we should
always think twice before releasing something as cheap 
shareware. Please consider first, if it is really worth
the shareware fee! 

It makes no sense to ask for 2 pounds shareware fee. 
It's too much trouble for everyone changing
this in a bank into the right currency, buying an envelope,
stamps and hoping that it will really arrive at the authors location.

Free the AMIGA!  Keep the freeware attitude alive!

 

